        <abstract> 
<p>A new edition [4th German] of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> to be published by Schweizerbart. JVC asks CD to send any changes or additions.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> has sold two-thirds of the first printing [1868].</p>  
<p>Hopes he may do translation of CD’s new work [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
